The Cove;;94;;95;;PG-13;;In Taiji, Japan, local fishermen hide a gruesome secret: the capture and slaughter of dolphins. Activist Ric O'Barry, who trained dolphins for the "Flipper" TV series, joins forces with filmmaker Louis Psihoyos and the Ocean Preservation Society to expose the brutal practice, risking life and limb in the process.;;Documentary;;Louie Psihoyos;;2009;;Hayden Panettiere,Isabel Lucas,Louie Psihoyos;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1208882-cove